6160,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:06:51.000Z","msg":"Ready<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動送頭<br />\n港島遊行集會送頭<br />\n深夜整連儂牆送頭<br />\n派傳單都會畀藍絲割肚不了<br />\n<br />\n而家我哋打旗號叫政府封關阻肺炎呀<br />\n民建聯都唔會夠膽出聲反對啦 粉嶺單野政府都hea應啦<br />\n<br />\n另外想問工會過咗咁多個月有幾多人入咗會？<br />\n全民大三罷？<br />\n唔好話無限期啦 就算一日 短期內我都睇唔出我哋有咩條件做得到 到時幾多生化人入咗關？再搞無限期三罷已經遲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為到時已經有唔少香港人奶咗野 咁醫護仲點罷工呀</span><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦送頭<br />\n你話畀我知唔送頭仲可以點"},{"pid":"7dd043c81c60a5c3f70f04b0f8f1f012c25e9c5d","tid":1846160,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:38:59.000Z","msg":"完全無事喎<br />\n暴乜動<br />\n根本over reaction<br />\n<br />\n等我隔離鄰舍感染到再緊張啦"},{"pid":"2352f4f6f93109468ccbe2342bc78f73389884e2","tid":1846160,"uid":1781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:41:54.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a71c4c485c5f09ceef48578a01918688c53573e","tid":1846160,"uid":